Package pizzapazza.filler

The filler package; a filler is an object able to fill an image by means of a color
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Z4AbstractBoundaryBehaviorFiller
    A Filler with a boundary behavior
    Z4AbstractEllipseInscribedFiller
    A Filler which can be inscribed in an ellipse
    Z4AbstractFiller
    The common abstract object for all fillers; each instance of Z4AbstractFiller provides a different painting style (radial, conic, elliptic, ect.)
    Z4ConicFiller
    A (multi) conic filler
    Z4EllipticFiller
    A (multi) elliptic filler
    Z4LinearFiller
    A (multi) linear filler
    Z4PolygonFiller
    A (multi) polygon filler
    Z4SpiralFiller
    A (multi) spiral filler
    Z4StarFiller
    A (multi) star filler
